@startuml
title Historical playback
autonumber

actor User
participant "PlaybackToolbarComponent" as Toolbar
participant "PlaybackStore" as Store
participant "HistoryApiClient" as ApiClient
participant "HistoryEndpoints" as Endpoint
participant "HistoryQueryService" as Query
participant "InMemoryTimelineStore" as Timeline

User -> Toolbar: Turn live mode off
Toolbar -> Store: setLive(false)
Store -> ApiClient: loadHistory(selectedSymbols, points)
ApiClient -> Endpoint: GET /api/history
Endpoint -> Query: getHistory(symbols, points)
Query -> Timeline: readWindow(symbols, points)
Timeline --> Query: HistoricalQuoteDto[]
Query --> Endpoint: HistoryResponse
Endpoint --> ApiClient: HistoryResponse
ApiClient --> Store: historyBySymbol

User -> Toolbar: Move scrub slider
Toolbar -> Store: setPlaybackIndex(index)
Store -> Store: recompute DisplayedStockRow[]

@enduml
